@shrshore this will avoid the inf value, the test seems to have failed because the python 3.5 build crashed with a cryptic message:

gcc-4.8: internal compiler error: Killed (program cc1plus)
Please submit a full bug report,
with preprocessed source if appropriate.

error: command 'ccache' failed with exit status 4
The command "python setup.py install" failed and exited with 1 during .

I will try to close and re-open the issue to see if it kicks off the build again.
